        },
        {
          "label": "(8)",
          "token": "8",
          "kind": "numeric",
          "text": "The commission may adopt rules to establish additional procedural and substantive requirements for review of changes to comprehensive plans and land use regulations adopted by local governments to implement a regional problem-solving agreement under ORS 197.652 to 197.658.",
